1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:40,000
(Watch on www.kisskh.li Support Admin)

2
00:00:47,292 --> 00:00:49,586
To make Bloody Week more exciting

3
00:00:49,962 --> 00:00:52,256
look inside your lockers.

4
00:00:54,007 --> 00:00:59,303
You'll find the names you have to kill
before the time runs out.

5
00:00:59,304 --> 00:01:01,347
If you don't get a name

6
00:01:01,348 --> 00:01:03,600
