7
00:01:04,852 --> 00:01:05,852
Mia!

8
00:01:07,146 --> 00:01:07,855
- Mia?
- Mia!

9
00:01:07,856 --> 00:01:10,356
Mia!

10
00:01:10,357 --> 00:01:11,400
Jerome, I know you.

11
00:01:12,025 --> 00:01:14,278
You're not capable of killing anyone.

12
