You just defended yourself.

13
00:01:15,988 --> 00:01:17,090
You didn't do anything wrong.

14
00:01:17,114 --> 00:01:18,073
This is an emergency.

15
00:01:18,115 --> 00:01:19,366
Open the door!

16
00:01:19,533 --> 00:01:20,659
I'm sorry but

17
00:01:21,368 --> 00:01:22,888
this is an order from
the headmistress.

18
00:01:24,288 --> 00:01:26,123
Open the clinic!

19
00:01:27,082 --> 00:01:28,082
If I were you

20
00:01:29,251 --> 00:01:31,003
I'll use my courage elsewhere.

21
00:01:31,170 --> 00:01:32,421
Not for this menial reason.

22
00:01:34,256 --> 00:01:35,256
I hope

23
00:01:37,009 --> 00:01:38,135
she was worth it.

24
00:01:43,265 --> 00:01:44,767
It's Mia's life.

25
00:01:48,061 --> 00:01:49,521
Just tell me my punishment.

26
00:01:51,273 --> 00:01:52,691
Death.

27
00:02:02,618 --> 00:02:03,869
Tonight.

28
00:02:04,620 --> 00:02:06,330
I will introduce to all of you

29
00:02:06,622 --> 00:02:09,373
the new co-leader of the
Black Blood Gang...

30
00:02:09,374 --> 00:02:10,501
Raise your voices

31
00:02:10,667 --> 00:02:12,461
for Matthew!

32
00:02:26,850 --> 00:02:29,102
Well, well, well...

33
00:02:29,853 --> 00:02:31,897
We have a visitor, boss.

34
00:02:32,105 --> 00:02:33,314
He said he won't leave

35
00:02:33,315 --> 00:02:34,524
until he talks with you.

36
00:02:34,525 --> 00:02:35,596
Wait.

37
00:02:37,736 --> 00:02:40,614
Did you really give this
arrogant ass a chance?

38
00:02:41,281 --> 00:02:43,742
And you allowed him
to enter our hideout?

39
00:02:44,743 --> 00:02:45,743
Show him out.

40
00:02:45,994 --> 00:02:47,037
What do you need?

41
00:02:47,538 --> 00:02:50,207
I'm here to talk to you.

42
00:02:52,876 --> 00:02:55,087
I want to join your gang.

43
00:03:00,717 --> 00:03:02,344
Do you think it's easy to join our gang?

44
00:03:02,553 --> 00:03:03,953
That you'll just sign an attendance

45
00:03:04,429 --> 00:03:05,639
and you’re magically a member?

46
00:03:13,897 --> 00:03:16,495
I hope you can forgive my
boys for greeting you harshly.

47
00:03:17,693 --> 00:03:19,069
Why are you here again?

48
00:03:25,603 --> 00:03:27,480
I want to join the Black Blood Gang.

49
00:03:28,638 --> 00:03:30,014
Why not?

50
00:03:31,248 --> 00:03:33,417
We need as many
members as we can get.

51
00:03:34,209 --> 00:03:35,209
I say...

52
00:03:36,420 --> 00:03:38,714
let's give him a chance.

53
00:03:40,936 --> 00:03:42,271
Matthew Hart.

54
00:03:43,594 --> 00:03:45,888
I commend your courage
coming here on your own.

55
00:03:46,388 --> 00:03:47,890
Specially during Bloody Night.

56
00:03:49,850 --> 00:03:51,184
I want to know your reason.

57
00:04:01,361 --> 00:04:02,361
Oh?

58
00:04:02,946 --> 00:04:04,066
Why did you become so quiet?

59
00:04:09,119 --> 00:04:10,119
Fine

60
00:04:11,204 --> 00:04:13,624
let's make it more simple.

61
00:04:14,750 --> 00:04:15,792
In one word

62
00:04:16,919 --> 00:04:18,820
what do you want
that we can offer?

63
00:04:20,683 --> 00:04:21,767
Power.

64
00:04:26,714 --> 00:04:27,714
Power.

65
00:04:30,307 --> 00:04:32,059
But power is not given.

66
00:04:34,144 --> 00:04:35,144
It should be earned.

67
00:04:37,189 --> 00:04:39,358
Well, well, well...

68
00:04:43,737 --> 00:04:44,737
you know

69
00:04:45,614 --> 00:04:47,950
all of us did our own
fair share of bloodshed

70
00:04:48,575 --> 00:04:51,036
before we got accepted here.

71
00:04:52,871 --> 00:04:54,331
What I want to say is

72
00:04:56,541 --> 00:04:58,502
you need to defeat me

73
00:04:59,127 --> 00:05:00,127
but of course

74
00:05:01,421 --> 00:05:03,465
don't cry if you lose, alright?

75
00:05:10,305 --> 00:05:11,974
You need to defeat Luke

76
00:05:12,179 --> 00:05:15,608
before you get the chance to be
a member of this brotherhood.

77
00:05:16,144 --> 00:05:18,522
Luke will not go easy on you.

78
00:05:19,898 --> 00:05:20,898
What now?

79
00:05:21,441 --> 00:05:22,609
Are you scared already?

80
00:05:24,653 --> 00:05:26,822
Do you want to go back to your dorm?

81
00:05:28,573 --> 00:05:29,824
One more word from you

82
00:05:29,825 --> 00:05:32,034
and your hair will not be the
only thing that'll be red tonight.

83
00:05:32,035 --> 00:05:33,912
- Ooh.
- Okay.

84
00:05:34,663 --> 00:05:35,789
Move, guys.

85
00:05:41,128 --> 00:05:42,713
Luke, don't embarrass us.

86
00:05:44,423 --> 00:05:45,583
Show him how it's done, Luke.

87
00:05:50,387 --> 00:05:51,387
Alright.

88
00:06:49,112 --> 00:06:50,112
That's it?

89
00:08:53,315 --> 00:08:56,527
Why? Why did you have to do this?

90
00:08:57,282 --> 00:08:58,408
I hate you!

91
00:09:01,372 --> 00:09:03,415
You're too noisy.

92
00:09:04,497 --> 00:09:05,874
Mind your own business!

93
00:09:07,834 --> 00:09:08,834
Raze...

94
00:09:14,758 --> 00:09:15,842
Don't you know

95
00:09:18,136 --> 00:09:20,680
it's not safe for a lady

96
00:09:21,556 --> 00:09:23,350
to be out here at night.

97
00:09:26,728 --> 00:09:28,355
The way you look at me...

98
00:09:32,108 --> 00:09:33,693
are you afraid of me?

99
00:09:38,949 --> 00:09:41,034
You shouldn't be afraid of me

100
00:09:42,476 --> 00:09:44,520
because he's scarier.

101
00:09:47,037 --> 00:09:50,499
He is the man you would
never want to challenge.

102
00:09:52,462 --> 00:09:54,047
Who are you talking about?

103
00:09:58,093 --> 00:10:00,053
I know what's bothering you.

104
00:10:02,305 --> 00:10:03,305
Fuck this.

105
00:10:05,225 --> 00:10:09,604
Did they really think
a newbie can kill me?

106
00:10:10,188 --> 00:10:12,482
Don’t you dare touch Matt.

107
00:10:14,985 --> 00:10:16,736
Why do you still trust him?

108
00:10:18,655 --> 00:10:20,156
He betrayed you

109
00:10:21,449 --> 00:10:22,951
and your friends

110
00:10:23,868 --> 00:10:25,412
