111
00:10:27,455 --> 00:10:28,789
He must have a reason...

112
00:10:28,790 --> 00:10:29,791
A reason?

113
00:10:32,460 --> 00:10:33,628
What could it be?

114
00:10:36,339 --> 00:10:38,466
Or maybe you can
give me a reason?

115
00:10:41,594 --> 00:10:42,594
What?

116
00:10:44,681 --> 00:10:48,560
Give me a reason
not to kill him.

117
00:10:52,856 --> 00:10:53,856
Well...

118
00:10:55,066 --> 00:10:56,900
