me a reason then...

119
00:10:56,901 --> 00:10:57,901
Me!

120
00:10:59,821 --> 00:11:01,072
Because of me!

121
00:11:03,408 --> 00:11:04,492
Because of you?

122
00:11:06,119 --> 00:11:08,121
Maybe you are a valid reason.

123
00:11:12,250 --> 00:11:13,460
You know why?

124
00:11:15,712 --> 00:11:18,298
Because you are giving us something.

125
00:11:21,009 --> 00:11:22,177
Something?

126
00:11:27,682 --> 00:11:30,685
It's possible that you'll be
the reason why I won't kill him.

127
00:11:33,688 --> 00:11:36,107
It's possible that you
are still an asset to us.

128
00:11:38,568 --> 00:11:40,362
Or maybe you're deadweight?

129
00:11:43,948 --> 00:11:45,450
