183
00:20:36,397 --> 00:20:37,440
Hoy.

184
00:20:42,570 --> 00:20:44,530
You're a lot of things, Ms. Shion.

185
00:20:44,697 --> 00:20:47,033
But I didn't think corny
was gonna be one of them.

186
00:20:48,784 --> 00:20:49,994
