190
00:20:57,919 --> 00:20:59,045
Hoy.

191
00:20:59,253 --> 00:21:00,338
Hoy!

192
00:21:01,088 --> 00:21:02,256
Hoy!

193
00:21:02,798 --> 00:21:03,798
Right?

194
00:21:12,975 --> 00:21:14,393
