today with your looks.

208
00:22:05,069 --> 00:22:07,195
I think it's your hair.

209
00:22:07,196 --> 00:22:08,447
Did you comb it?

210
00:22:09,323 --> 00:22:11,993
I really don’t know what
you're talking about, Ms. Shion.

211
