266
00:25:59,470 --> 00:26:00,804
Please kill me!

267
00:26:02,139 --> 00:26:03,139
Please.

268
00:26:03,933 --> 00:26:05,309
Just this once.

269
00:26:07,937 --> 00:26:08,937
Zein...

270
00:26:12,942 --> 00:26:13,692
Please.

271
00:26:13,693 --> 00:26:14,901
Kill me!

272
00:26:14,902 --> 00:26:15,944
No!

273
00:26:15,945 --> 00:26:18,655
- Kill me now!
- I can't!

274
00:26:18,656 --> 00:26:20,073
No!

275
00:26:20,074 --> 00:26:21,825
I don't want to.

276
00:26:23,410 --> 00:26:24,410
Please...

277
00:26:25,913 --> 00:26:27,998
just this once, please.

278
00:26:39,635 --> 00:26:40,635
Fine.

279
00:26:41,345 --> 00:26:42,429
Fine.

280
00:26:43,138 --> 00:26:44,348
Just this once.

281
00:27:38,944 --> 00:27:39,944
Hoy!

282
00:27:48,120 --> 00:27:50,873
